Package: r4apl
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Analysis and Processing Data for APL with Focus on GC-MS/TCD/FID, IC & HPLC
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Markus", "Kurtz", email = "markus.kurtz@apl-landau.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The 'r4apl' package provides a suite of tools for processing data from various analytical techniques, 
    including Gas Chromatography-Mass Spectrometry (GC-MS), Flame Ionization Detection (GC-FID), 
    Thermal Conductivity Detection (GC-TCD), Ion Chromatography (IC), and High-Performance Liquid Chromatography (HPLC). 
    Additional functions for data analysis and visualization across these platforms are also included.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 1.1.0),
    tidyr (>= 1.2.1),
    data.table (>= 1.14.0),
    plotly
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    ggplot2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
